The paper proposes a hybrid neural model for deep question-answering task from history examinations, which involves effective representation to capture complicated semantic relations between questions and answers. This suggests that the paper may belong to the natural language processing (NLP) field, which is covered by several arXiv CS sub-categories. Specifically, cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as it covers NLP and machine learning topics. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) are also likely categories as they cover machine learning and deep learning topics. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is another possible category as it covers techniques for retrieving relevant information from large collections of text. Finally, cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is a less likely category but still possible as it covers neural network and deep learning topics.
